dc_title_s: Ann Arbor quadrangle, Michigan: topography; Jno. H. Renshawe, geographer in charge.
dc_description_s: Relief indicated by contours and spot heights. Dated: April 1904. Surveyed in 1901-02. 1 map: col.; 45 x 35 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
